                <p>Tahminsel analitik, makine öğrenimi pipeline'ları, gerçek zamanlı BI dashboard'ları ve veri mühendisliği ile verilerinizi değere dönüştürüyoruz.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Services" class="service-link">
                    Detaylar
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card" data-aos data-aos-delay="160">
                <div class="service-icon service-icon-amber">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Stratejik Danışmanlık</h3>
                <p>Teknoloji yol haritası, AI adopsiyon stratejisi ve dijital dönüşüm danışmanlığıyla organizasyonunuzu geleceğe hazırlıyoruz.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Services" class="service-link">
                    Detaylar
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card" data-aos data-aos-delay="0">
                <div class="service-icon service-icon-blue">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Yazılım Geliştirme</h3>
                <p>Özel ihtiyaçlarınıza yönelik yüksek performanslı yazılım çözümleri. .NET 8, React, Node.js ve mikroservis mimarileriyle kurumsal uygulamalar.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Services" class="service-link">
                    Detaylar
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card" data-aos data-aos-delay="80">
                <div class="service-icon service-icon-green">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Bulut & DevOps</h3>
                <p>AWS, Azure ve GCP'de ölçeklenebilir altyapı mimarileri. Kubernetes, CI/CD pipeline'ları ve Infrastructure as Code ile maliyet optimizasyonu.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Services" class="service-link">
                    Detaylar
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card" data-aos data-aos-delay="160">
                <div class="service-icon service-icon-red">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Siber Güvenlik</h3>
                <p>Penetrasyon testleri, 7/24 SOC hizmeti ve Zero Trust mimarisiyle dijital varlıklarınızı sürekli koruma altında tutuyoruz.</p>
                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Services" class="service-link">
                    Detaylar
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

